transcript:
Customer: Mera mulk, mera desh, mera yeh watan.

Hello.

Executive: Haan ji. Haan Javed sir pahunch gaye aap office? Haan ji, pahuncha hun, bataiye.
Customer: Achcha, aap bataiye sir kya change karwana hai? Koi jo change karwana hai na, woh aapke samne hi main kar dunga sir. Jo bhi aapko theek nahi lag raha hai usme.
Customer: Wohi toh dikkat aa rahi hai mujhe bhai sahab. Ek keyword woh toh main change karaun usko.
Customer: Jo keyword diye the, us keyword mein jo hai koi detail nahi bhari hai, kisi mein photo nahi dala hai.
Customer: Kisi mein keyword nahi dala hai.
Executive: Aapke paas, aapke paas jo photos aapne diye the, woh pade hain kya abhi bhi?
Customer: Nahi bhai sahab, mere se koi baat hi nahi hui photo ki. Mere se yeh kaha gaya tha, sara kuch hum kara ke denge, photo vagera sab kuch.
Executive: Achcha, photo vagera aapne kuch nahi diya apni side se?
Customer: Na, na, na.
Executive: Ek baar aap meeting pe aake bata do ki kya kya change karwana hai aapko, fir main apni side se change kar dunga woh.
Customer: Are bhaiya, tumne us din phone kara tha mujhe yaad hoga shayad, maine yeh kaha tha ke ek jagah jo hai point seven ton likh ke aa raha hai aur uska price humne dal diya jyada.
Customer: Aapne bola tha, theek hai sir main kar dunga. Teen char din tak woh nahi ho paya tha. Toh fir maine apne aap woh fir call aayi thi toh maine karaya tha woh.
Executive: Point seven wale ki baat kar rahe hain?
Customer: Woh jo Hitachi ka jo likh hua tha point seven ton.
Executive: Yaad hai? Woh toh uska, uska toh mail usi time kar diya tha sir maine.
Customer: Toh mail kise kar diya tha?
Executive: Jo production team hoti hai na, usko mail kar diya tha usi time pe maine. Aap kya rahenge isme? Aapka, aapka kya sahyog rahega?
Executive: Sir yahan pe hamara jo rehta hai na, jaise kuch error aa raha hai, jaise ek product hai aapka abhi 20,000 CFM Hitachi unit.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Theek hai? Isme aap prices aapne dale hain 18,000 per ton ke hisab se. Yahi price dal rakhe hain aapne?
Customer: Aur usme jo hai error aa raha hai red color ka.
Executive: Haan, woh error isliye aa raha hai kyunki koi bhi agar matlab AC vagera lagti hai toh woh pieces ke hisab se lagti hai. Aapne wahan pe ton ke hisab se dal rakhi hai.
Customer: Pieces ke hisab se kyun lagegi bhai AC?
Executive: Sir jo aap ton dalenge na, woh specification mein dalenge. Specification jo side mein aate hain.
Customer: Toh yahan par kya dalenge, piece?
Executive: Yahan pe sir aap price jo daloge na, woh toh piece ke hisab se daloge. Ek example ke taur pe main aapko batata hun. Aap kuch bhi product. Are ek minute rukiye, main aapko ek number mera jo hai ek 94 wala number hai?
Executive: Ek minute.
Executive: Nahi mere paas nahi hai 94 wala number.
Customer: Aapke paas nahi hai? Meri jo profile pe hai.
Executive: But woh mujhe dikhega nahi na. Mujhe do number dikhenge yahan pe. 90217 last mein ek aur ek 93264 last mein.
Customer: Haan.
Customer: Maine us din number aapke samne hi toh change karwaya tha. Woh aap video meet pe se maine hi toh change karwaya tha aapka number.
Executive: Woh change aapke bol rahe the aap?
Customer: Woh aapne kahan karaye the? Maine khud karaye hain phone karke fir bhai.
Executive: Phone karke? Are sir maine. Number change karaye the, email change karaye the maine. Fir jo hai fir woh number change kare the.
Executive: Sir Google Meet pe aap mere samne hi toh change kiye hain aapne. Maine bataya tha. Ek cheez dekho bhai, main pehli baat toh yeh hai ki main aapko baar baar time nahi de paunga. Mere liye bahut dikkat hoti hai. Ek number note karo aap mera jo profile dusra kyunki ispe net nahi chalta sir. Aap mere se kaho ispe aa jao, uspe aa jao, dikkat ho jayegi mujhe.
Executive: Barao number.
Customer: Number diya aapne office wala?
Customer: 94.
Executive: Okay.
Customer: 94.
Executive: 9457777.
Customer: 9457777 524.
Executive: 524.
Executive: Theek hai.
Customer: Ispe call kariye aap mere ko. Ab isse aage badh baat karte hain.
Executive: Ispe call karun?
Customer: Haan.
Executive: Theek hai. Koi aur dusra number hai? Rukiye hold kariye zara.
Customer: Okay, okay.
Customer: Zubair.
Customer: Zubair.
Customer: Zubair.
Customer: Ho gaya kya?
Customer: Boliye.
Customer: Isko mobile lijiye mobile 90 wala.
Customer: Ye kya requirement aayi hai? Thoda ye kya hai?
Customer: Aur ye toh aayi is mahine.
Customer: Hello.
Executive: Ji.
Customer: Isme net chalega nahi na.
Customer: Opening opening kharab hai.
Customer: Ye toh deal ho gayi.
Customer: Purani call hai.
Customer: Saath mein delivery call karani hai. Delivery karani hai ki nahi toh bataiye kyunki yahan se humne payment kar di.
Customer: Saath mein delivery hai. Aur ye panch delivery hai. Baki delivery.
Customer: Agar abhi se delivery nahi aayi na toh manzil mein kuch nahi hoga.
Customer: Aise hi hoga toh kaise delivery hoga?
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Hmm number bataiye apna. 90.
Customer: 90.
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Last mein 217 hai na last mein?
Customer: 217 hai last mein?
Customer: Haan 217 hai.
Executive: Haan inka number toh add hai na. Yeh Zubair wagera ke number iske baad mein add karwaya tha sir.
Customer: Theek hai, theek hai. Aapne aaj karaya. Chalo aap call kariye.
summary:
Concerns:

- Wants to change a keyword.

- Details missing in keywords, no photos.

- Price showing per ton instead of per piece.



Resolution:

- Executive asked to share changes in meeting.

- Executive shared production team was emailed.

- Executive confirmed Zubair's number is added.



Next Steps: 

- Customer will call on new number.



Alert (If Any):

None

@@@Sentiment:

- Angry -> Satisfied



@@@Key Topics:

- keywords, profile, price, number change
